name: Sel Maa
content:
Sel Maa was a female Near-Human socialite in the Coruscant nightclub scene during the last decades of the Galactic Republic. A renowned flirt, Sel Maa spent much of her time within the Outlander Club's dark alcoves with Daro Willits. Maa's skin was a pattern of rainbow colored ribbons that stretched up to her face and capped by a large truss of blond curls.
The actress playing Sel Maa, in costume, introduced the twelfth episode of the Episode II behind-the-scenes video series on location.
